Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.06,0:00:05.19,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,小面包  在的话就动一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.40,0:00:10.53,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,告诉我埃米莉可在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.86,0:00:12.99,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凯特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.08,0:00:18.08,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凯特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.41,0:00:19.20,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,埃米莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.58,0:00:21.16,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我在这里  凯特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:27.96,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,埃米莉可  你在哪  你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:33.01,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,埃米莉可！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.89,0:00:38.22,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,没事吧  现在给你松开
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.43,0:00:40.43,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凯特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.89,0:00:44.27,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你没事真是太好了  现在马上从这里出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.44,0:00:46.27,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不是的  凯特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.69,0:00:47.69,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.56,0:00:50.86,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.03,0:00:55.20,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凯特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.66,0:00:57.53,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,爱德华
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.99,0:01:01.95,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,可算没让我白等啊  凯特
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.37,0:01:04.29,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我就知道你肯定会来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.66,0:01:07.38,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,毕竟你是为活人偶着想的影家人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:10.25,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你的目标一开始就是我对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.67,0:01:18.34,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,到了早上你就会作为影宅的叛乱分子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.47,0:01:20.64,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,被带到伟大的祖父大人面前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.10,0:01:24.98,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,这样的话我就能实现我的夙愿  晋升进入三楼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:29.27,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,来吧凯特  回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.73,0:01:33.86,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你在谋划什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:39.24,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你以为不说话还能逃得掉吗  看来你还没明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.57,0:01:44.37,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,就算你不是叛乱分子  我也可以告发你违反规则
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.54,0:01:48.62,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,告发你穿着这身衣服出现在祖父大人这一栋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.63,0:01:52.25,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,, 凯特是来救被你拐走的埃米莉可…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:54.38,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你觉得这么说会有人信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.13,0:01:57.59,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,身为大人的我和身为儿童的你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.88,0:02:01.35,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,伟大的祖父大人会相信谁  答案很明显
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.06,0:02:07.06,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,一开始就已经分出胜负了  凯特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:14.82,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那么慢慢等待伟大的祖父大人醒来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.74,0:02:18.11,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你一定会受到严重的处罚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.57,0:02:21.28,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,这说不定会是你的最后一杯红茶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.33,0:02:28.00,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,死心吧  你已经完了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:04.03,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凯特  我现在去帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.63,0:04:39.63,Shadow house-title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(397,517)\pos(1698,866.667)}为了影宅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.09,0:04:40.96,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,在几楼来着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:48.35,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:56.56,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,什么啊  好可怕  到一边去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:05:00.86,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,乔恩…我在找爱德华的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:06.03,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,叫我跟上去？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.41,0:05:07.70,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我怎么会上你的当…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:13.29,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,多了两台推车  也就是说侵入者有两个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:14.91,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,保持警戒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:19.04,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我去向爱德华传达  杰勒德搜查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:22.09,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,他们应该是混入到无面人偶之中了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:30.30,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我…我去搜查侵入者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:31.76,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:37.73,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.45,0:05:52.45,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,这样你就干不了坏事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:06.34,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:14.14,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:19.85,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,把他们全都当作叛乱分子交上去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:24.23,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,这样我们肯定能去三楼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:33.74,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,有在做好孩子吗  看来终于放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:39.79,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,反抗影宅是愚蠢至极的行为  现在就算后悔也太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:44.38,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,最后的红茶要凉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:48.26,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,抱歉  你这样绑着喝不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:56.43,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:00.39,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:01.06,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,埃米莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:05.27,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,喂  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:13.99,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不对  是乔恩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:16.08,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,乔恩少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.24,0:07:17.66,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你是来帮我的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:21.42,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,当然  不过现在乔恩也需要帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:24.00,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:27.09,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,又是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:30.26,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,这孩子是我们的同伴  赶紧跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:38.18,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,乔恩呢  找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:42.69,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,没有  果然是去那边帮凯特小姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:47.19,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,真是鲁莽  希望他不会拖后腿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:49.82,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那露薏丝和露呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:52.45,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,她们看起来很困的样子  回房间了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:54.45,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,一个两个都是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:08:00.83,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,顺利的话是时候该回来了吧  好担心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:03.92,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,对不起让您担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:08.92,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不过我相信乔恩少爷  他肯定会带着她们回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:11.80,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,恐怕到那个时候爱德华也会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:15.80,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那时才是帕利克少爷出场的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:17.97,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,要怎么阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.47,0:08:20.47,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不  这…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:23.81,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不好意思啊  我没什么厉害的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:34.66,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,可是  我觉得帕利克少爷想救伙伴的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:36.53,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是不会输给任何人的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:43.00,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,帕利克少爷最大的能力是勇敢美丽的心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:50.34,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是这样的话  那也是受到了你的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.76,0:08:53.09,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,「露面」的时候  是你流着泪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:56.30,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,拜托乔恩和尚恩去救帕利克
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.76,0:08:57.76,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,都是托你的福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.31,0:09:00.26,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,帕利克少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:10.52,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,屋顶？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:16.03,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不会是要从这里跳回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:23.25,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,相当远啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.25,0:09:25.25,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.38,0:09:36.93,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,停止无谓的抵抗  你们已经完了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.18,0:09:41.39,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,因为你们反抗影宅  擅自侵入这栋楼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:44.77,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,先来儿童楼的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:48.06,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你们说的话谁会信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:01.20,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凯特  带着埃米莉可飞起来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:02.83,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,乔恩  你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:04.50,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,别管我  快走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:06.50,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,在说什么乱七八糟的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:13.96,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,埃米莉可  紧紧抓住我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:15.42,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:27.89,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,放弃吧凯特  这不是以你的黑灰能力能过去的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:39.49,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,在中途坠落死亡  是适合愚蠢叛乱者的结局吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:41.12,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:48.83,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我怎么会让凯特死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:11:00.05,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,别小看乔恩我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:05.56,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,艾琳！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:15.11,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我怎么会让凯特死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:26.79,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,这样能飞到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:29.16,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凯特小姐  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.41,0:11:37.46,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,都怪我被抓住  给凯特小姐和乔恩少爷添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:40.55,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,现在就先别管那种事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.84,0:11:45.80,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,埃米莉可  不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:46.93,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凯特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.10,0:11:53.10,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,果然是出事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.35,0:11:55.90,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,能够返回的路应该只有这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.07,0:11:58.90,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:03.82,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.58,0:12:13.42,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凯特小姐  埃米莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:16.00,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,来这边  不要急慢慢来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:21.72,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:33.60,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.65,0:12:35.85,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,才不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:42.95,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,爱德华
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.66,0:12:45.74,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.66,0:12:53.87,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凯特  乔恩怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:57.67,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,乔恩用黑灰能力帮我们飞了过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:13:00.80,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,但是他可能因为反作用无法动弹了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:09.72,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凯特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:15.64,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,爱德华
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:18.06,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,尽给我找麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.94,0:13:25.15,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,这里是儿童栋  不会再让你为所欲为
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.65,0:13:29.78,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你们以为在和谁说话  搞清楚自己的立场
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:35.33,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,想在影宅里活下去  就舍弃掉无聊的同伴意识
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:39.63,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,死心吧  凯特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:45.55,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你们再这样碍事我就把你们全都处理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:47.93,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你这话是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:04.11,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你不是睡了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:08.32,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我转变心意啦  把芭芭拉叫过来可是大功一件
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.82,0:14:11.08,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,这样一来露薏丝就一定能进戴星组了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:13.08,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,真是露薏丝的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:15.08,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,难以想象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:20.54,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,和祖父大人同住的栋里的爱德华大人居然出现在儿童栋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:24.05,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,究竟是怎么回事  还请麻烦您说明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.51,0:14:27.26,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我作为儿童栋管理人 要对他们进行直接指导
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:30.43,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,这大清早的要指导什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.84,0:14:34.18,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,刚才还说要全部处理掉  我倒不觉得这是指导
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:41.48,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,就算你是管理人  擅自闯入儿童栋也是被禁止的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:45.86,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我已经向三楼的各位汇报了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:47.44,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:52.12,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,他们在走廊的尽头等着您
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:58.37,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,这全都托您的福
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:05.21,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,正因为有您「每天给我仔细巡逻」这般认真的指导
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:09.59,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我们才能揭发如此严重的违规行为
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:11.84,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:36.16,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,这次真的十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:39.87,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,事到如今才乖乖道歉已经来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.16,0:15:44.29,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,爱德华  你被影宅放逐了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:46.63,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,您是说放逐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:48.38,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,这不是当然的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:51.18,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,就算要给孩子们指导
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:54.85,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,但你居然进到儿童栋里拐走他们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.35,0:15:56.35,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:15:57.51,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不要狡辩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:16:02.81,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你可是个在「露面」里让「脸」胡思乱想的问题人物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.27,0:16:07.57,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,总之这个宅邸不需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.73,0:16:11.57,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,需要的只有对伟大的祖父大人有用的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.07,0:16:17.24,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,把爱德华放逐  剩下的两人降级到一楼如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:18.87,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,就这样决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:22.75,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,您意下如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.67,0:16:28.88,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,爱德华
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:34.13,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你对孩子们大胆又独特的指导  其实我很感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.89,0:16:38.72,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,但是这次你做得稍微过了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.02,0:16:48.69,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,包括爱德华在内的三人  给予严厉警告
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.99,0:16:58.08,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,听好了  下不为例
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:17:01.87,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是  今后我会继续精进努力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.47,0:17:17.01,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,处分是不是有点太便宜他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:24.31,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,影宅似乎还有很多种可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:34.15,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,总归是得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.70,0:17:37.36,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,但是这样一来离三楼更远了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:40.62,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,爱德华  不要再擅自行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:43.91,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我还没有放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:46.71,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,从这次宽容的决断来看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:49.21,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我感受到了他对我的期待和爱护
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:51.38,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,就算是为了回报这份心意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:57.13,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我也一定要把顽强又狡猾的反叛分子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:18:00.51,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,连同三楼的那群废物们一起赶出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.51,0:18:05.68,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,这全都是为了伟大的祖父大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.61,0:18:19.16,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,怎么了  埃米莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.53,0:18:23.70,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,没有  只是能光明正大地从房间里出来有点难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.95,0:18:27.16,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,而且能和凯特小姐并肩而行我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:28.42,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.37,0:18:33.21,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,说起来  乔恩少爷那之后怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:35.67,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,还不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:43.06,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,新人小姐  聚会至少应该早点到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:45.43,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,抱歉  大家到的都很早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.14,0:18:48.77,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,乔恩  你没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:51.94,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,其实那时我拼命抓住他回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.23,0:18:54.69,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,抓住爱德华骑的黑灰鸽子的尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.57,0:18:57.82,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,多亏了那个奇怪的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.36,0:19:00.49,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.20,0:19:05.95,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,说起来露薏丝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.62,0:19:14.59,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,美丽的蔷薇凯特  盛开的非洲菊露薏丝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:16.59,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,说明会要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.88,0:19:19.59,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,要学习宅邸里正确的生活方式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:21.59,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,嗯  请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.59,0:19:22.80,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.43,0:19:29.98,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凯特小姐  话说那个到底是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.19,0:19:31.56,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那个  是指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:36.98,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,就是那个帮了我们的  小小的很可爱的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.98,0:19:39.28,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那个啊  真是不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:43.41,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那孩子为什么会知道凯特能使用黑灰能力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:46.87,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凯特小姐  怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.66,0:19:48.58,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:01.36,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,这是重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:04.49,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,影族是优秀的贵族
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.74,0:21:08.99,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,活人偶为侍奉影族而感到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:20.88,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不可忘记要感谢影宅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:38.81,Shadow house-an8,,0,0,0,,拭けば明日は  すすが積もる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:38.81,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,即使擦去黑灰明天也会积攒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:43.94,Shadow house-an8,,0,0,0,,すすが積もれば  また拭ける
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:43.94,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,即使黑灰积攒也会再次擦去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.19,0:21:48.70,Shadow house-an8,,0,0,0,,さあ  働きましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.19,0:21:48.70,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,来工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.07,0:21:53.33,Shadow house-an8,,0,0,0,,お役に立ちましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.07,0:21:53.33,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,派上用场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.50,0:21:58.38,Shadow house-an8,,0,0,0,,余計なことは  考えない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.50,0:21:58.38,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,多余的事情  不去考虑
